er in a fractured, subjective world that mirrors the inner lives of its characters.\n\n#JapaneseCinema #FilmHistory #SilentFilm\n#Cinephile#APageOfMadness #ExperimentalFilm #AvantGardeCinema #CultCinema#FilmReel #ArthouseFilm #WorldCinema", "duration": 28.133, "timestamp": 1768569103, "uploader_id": "77832814550", "uploader": "Film Paranoia", "channel": "film.paranoia", "like_count": 25704, "comment_count": 147, "comments": [{"author": "justicedontkno", "author_id": "58223759064", "id": "18071322317256516", "text": "", "timestamp": 1775150111}, {"author": "judyblooms_vegasbeautypmu", "author_id": "74117029836", "id": "18058820408651029", "text": "@c.l.u.b.classics  this genre I was telling you about", "timestamp": 1774820322}, {"author": "davidarthurwalterz", "author_id": "58520078103", "id": "18199443070351710", "text": "It doesn't sound silent.", "timestamp": 1774697184}, {"author": "samcaya", "author_id": "509773161", "id": "17988908492955688", "text": "Is it yoko's mom", "timestamp": 1774650875}, {"author": "artsofoul", "author_id": "49650252326", "id": "18068398169310841", "text": "These cuts are insane", "timestamp": 1774549091}, {"author": "feedingtuberecords_rozztoxart", "author_id": "51900664", "id": "17909844030363281", "text": "One of my favorites ❤️", "timestamp": 1774380388}, {"author": "my_wave79", "author_id": "2220278065", "id": "17876385387554577", "text": "@dafcarballo", "timestamp": 1774314565}, {"author": "jvoneisenbachhalter", "author_id": "6053722235", "id": "18573389242041954", "text": "How Trump's brain looks inside. 😄", "timestamp": 1774307149}, {"author": "fegzytourist", "author_id": "80249264228", "id": "18216261589316370", "text": "Pretentious noncery", "timestamp": 1774256496}, {"author": "michael_simic_", "author_id": "2062475024", "id": "17931287166214532", "text": "❤️❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1774166946}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/617868225_17856997986598551_6676559314010475970_n.jpg?